<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="V" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Volley1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Volley,</orth> subst. a discharge of many firearms at once: <bibl n="shak. jn 5.5.5" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 5, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.363" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 363</bibl>. Metaphorically: <cit><quote>a fine v. of words, and quickly shot off,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 4, 33</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>